headline: Software Development Stocks Q3 Teardown: PagerDuty (NYSE:PD) Vs The Rest
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how PagerDuty (NYSE:PD) and the rest of the software development stocks fared in Q3.
